                            <comment id="13059095" author="ivaynberg" created="Sat, 2 Jul 2011 18:39:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;attaching a patch with a failing unit test, dont have time right now to fix the actual problem...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13059189" author="mgrigorov" created="Sun, 3 Jul 2011 12:12:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The test is added to 1.5.x to protect from regressions.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13059198" author="jdonnerstag" created="Sun, 3 Jul 2011 13:36:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this has been fixed in 1.5 with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-3833&quot; title=&quot;Components inside an invisible &amp;lt;wicket:enclosure&amp;gt; are still rendered&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-3833&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-3833&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13059199" author="mgrigorov" created="Sun, 3 Jul 2011 13:44:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s not fixed in 1.4.x.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13059203" author="jdonnerstag" created="Sun, 3 Jul 2011 14:25:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch requires changes which are allowed in 1.4 only to fix severe bugs. On the other hand inline enclosures have only been added recently to 1.4. I suggest to apply the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
